name: GlcNAc
comment: PMID: 2525556 by MT.  GNT6 only makes penta-antennary; i.e. requires previous GlcNAc addition to 6-position of 6-linked Man (by GNT5).  Activity not yet detected in mammals.  Activity reported in chicken oviduct.  But even in chicken the triantennary glycan (4-substitution without 6-substititutioni) is not allowed
